lead_paragraph: American journeyman Brian Stuard birdied four of his last nine holes to seize a one-shot lead when the weather-delayed second round of the Zurich Classic of New Orleans was completed on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Stuard Leads in New Orleans at Halfway Point
